 ‹Mintiʼ in najbʼen tbʼi tuʼn aju tzʼaqli, ex mintiʼ in xi tqʼoʼn ambʼil tuʼn tkubʼ tzʼibʼet moqa tuʼn t-xi qʼamet›, chi
Aragorn. ‹Ex mintiʼ in najbʼen saq tuʼn. Aye Orcs toj aq´untl te Barad-dur n-chi ajb´en kye
