 ‹¡At jun txʼolbʼabʼil nya bʼaʼn tuʼn t-xi qʼamet!›. chi Legolas. ‹Oʼkx at kabʼe bark tibʼaj
k'ulb'il pwaq. Mintiʼ kanet jun techel quʼne tiʼj juntl».
 '¿Ope che ten Orcs atztzu?' xi tqanin Aragorn.
 ‹Mintiʼ o tzʼok qkeʼyine jun techel kyiʼj, chi Gimli xi ttzaqʼweʼn. 'exttzen aye orcos n-chi tzaj ky-k´amo´n moqa
kub´ t-xiten kykyaqil bark, extzen aye ky-q´ob´.
 'Ok n-ka´yine twitz tx´otx´ aj q-pone atz, chi Aragorn.
 Jalin tzaj kyq´o´n Boromir toj tmij bark a t-xi´ q´i´n. A
t-xb´alun gris extzen elven-cloak n-chi kub´ ky-xmo´n extzen n-chi kyq´o´n tjaq´ twi´. N-chi ky-b´inchen
aju ttzmal twiʼ qʼeq ex nim twaʼlil ex ok tqʼoʼn tibʼaj t-xuʼk. A t-xu´k q´an pwaq te Lorien
n-chi qoptz´aj ti´j t-xu´k. A t-xu´k n-chi kyq´o´n ttxlaj, extzen t-xe t-xu´k n-chi kyq´o´n
aju cach b'aj pa'n tib' tuk'ix qe t-xu'k ex qe t-xaq t-spad; tjaq´ tqan n-chi kyq´o´n
spad kye aj q'oj ti'j. B'e'x ok kyk'alo'n t-xe' bark ti'j t-xe' juntl bark, ex ok kyq'o'n
etz tiʼn toj aʼ. N-chi b´et ky-b´is ttzi mar, extzen n-chi b´et ky-b´et toj
jun canal n-chi b´et t-xew n-chi ik´x ky-b´et twitz tx´otx´ te Parth Galen. Aye t-xaq t-xaq
te Tol Brandir n-chi qoptz´aj: jalin tmij aq´b´il. Tej kyxiʼ toj sur, aju qʼaqʼ
te Rauros n-chi jaw we´ extzen n-chi qoptz´aj ky-witz, jun t-xmakal q´anpwaq. A t-xilen extzen a tq´ajq´ajel
aye tzqij n-chi tzaj ky-xupin kyq´iq´ mya at kyq´iq´.
 Tuk´il b´is n-chi ky-etz ky-xo´n a bark te muqb´il: atzun Boromir n-chi kub´ t-ximan, t-xtalb´il, t-xob´il,
n-chi b´et tib´aj t-xu´k a´ n-chi b´et. A nima tzaj ti´n te akux n-chi ky-tzyu´n
ky-bark t-xe ky-b´e tuk´e ky-pale. N-chi b´et ky-txlaj, extzen cheb´e cheb´e t-bark
xi´, n-chi b´et toj jun qlolj twitz t-spik´umal q´anpwaq; extzen noq minab´en
