Aye orcos, aye ax ikx n-chi kyi´n ky-q´ob´ saq te Isengard: a t-xilen lu mas nim tipumal extzen mas tz´aq
kywitz kykyaqil txqantl.
 'Maske ikyjo, n-ku q-b´inchen jun b´ajsb´il kye. Extzun nimxix amb´il o qo ten najchaq. Aq´oye
