 'N-xi nq´o´ne chjonte teya ti´j tb´anil tyol,' chi Aragorn, 'exttzen a wanmiye taj tu´n n-xi´ye tuk´e
Aya; pero mlay bʼant tuʼn tkyaj ntzaqpiʼne qe wamiwe akux atx qʼuqbʼil nkʼuʼje».
 'A q´uqb´il kyk´u´j mya n-kyaj,' chi Eomer. Mlay che kanet qe tamiwa tuʼna toj Northborders.
 ‹Atzun qe wamiwe mintiʼ in che kyaj ten. N-kanet jun yek´b´il q´ancha´l qu´n mya najchaq ti´j muro te Oriente
