 'Aye q-amiwe n-chi ky-b´inchen ky-xb´alun ik tza´n qe, chi Aragorn; 'exttzen ma tz´el tpa´na qi´je
tjaq´ t-spik´umal q´ij.
 'Otoq tz´el naj ti´j nk´u´je, chi Eomer. ‹Kwest tuʼn tten qʼuqbʼil qkʼuʼj tiʼj jun tiʼ kyxol nimku xjal
b´is. A twitz tx´otx´ tkyaqil t-xilen t-xilen. Elf ex Enano junx n-chi b´et toj q-q´ij tkyaqil q´ij
