jun tb´anil spurt n-chi b´aj t-xilen tun t-xi´ t-xe jun b´etb´il. Yajxitl o til qa chʼixtaq tkubʼ tzʼaq qʼij;
n-ku tz´aq t-xe witz Misty; aye t-xlekumal n-chi pon twitz tx´otx´. Aye soldad te
A Mordor tzaj t-xo´n ky-wi´ extzen tzaj tzyet tu´n t-xi´ t-xo´n t-xew. A k´ul qlolj extzen
lamol. Ya otaq che ik´x kyi´j junjun tze´ t-xe´l. A tx´otx´ n-chi tzyet tu´n
t-xaq twitz kya´j. mas t-xe´; extzun aye orcos mya n-chi kub´ ky-k´u´j. Kykab´il Ugluk extzen
tzaj tq´ajq´ajel Grishnakh, n-chi tzaj tqona tun t-xi kyb´inchen jun b´ajsb´il aq´untl.
 ‹Ok chi bʼant kyuʼn. Ok chi el oq, chi Pippin xi t-ximin. extzen tzaj t-xnaq´tza´n
t-xupin t-xu´k, tun t-xi tka´yin t-xe tuk´e jun twitz tib´aj t-xu´k. Ok tka´yin qa
aye xjal n-chi b´et toj tjawitz q´ij ya otaq che ten junx kyuk´e aye orcos, n-chi b´et kyib´aj t-xe t-xaq a´. A
t-xe q´ij n-chi tzaj ky-q´o´n ky-lans extzen ky-casco, extzen n-chi q´ankyaq toj ky-wi´ n-chi b´et. Aqe
n-chi ky-okx ky-b´inchen aye orcos, n-chi tzaj ky-q´o´n ky-b´i´n tun mya n-chi b´et ky-xolx, extzen n-chi ky-q´o´n ky-b´e
aju t-xlekumal nima.
 N-chi ximenxix ti´j ti ky-b´inchb´en xjal. Tajtoq jaʼlo tuʼn tten
n-xnaq´tzan mas toj Rivendell, extzen n-ok tka´yin mas kyi´j mapa ex ti´chaq; pero tuj tq'ijlalil lu
aye t-xim te b´e n-chi tzaj ky-q´o´n ky-q´ob´ aye mas b´a´n, extzen myia b´i´n
n-ximan qa n-chi el tpa´n tib´ ti´j Gandalf, moqa ti´j Strider, extzen ti´j Frodo. Tkyaqil
aju n-chi tzaj tna´n ti´j Rohan, a tchej Gandalf, Shadowfax, tzaj tna´n
tzaja tuj tx'otx' lu. A jlu n-b´i´n te jun q´uqb´il kyk´u´j, ik tza´n t-xi´.
 'extzen tza´n tten k-xel ky-b´i´n qa mya Orcos qo´?' xi t-ximin. 'Mya n-ximane qa ma tz´ok kyq´o´n
ma tz´ok tb´i´na kyi´j hobbits tzalu. N-ximane qa b´a´n tu´n n-tzalaje tu´n ky-b´i´n aye orcos
ik tza'n ma chin kub' najsa'ne, noqtzun tu'nj, mas wajb'ile tu'n nklete.' Aye amb´il tzaj tqona
qa aye extzen a Merry n-chi kub´ b´yo´n junx kyuk´e aye n-chi tzyet ky-b´i´n, na´mxtoq ky-b´yo´n aye xjal te
A Rohan b´i´ntaqe kyi´j.
 Junjun kyxol qeju n-chi b´et kyib´aj chej n-chi yek´unte ky-b´i´n ky-b´i´n, b´a´n ky-b´i´n ky-b´i´n ky-b´i´n
kej. N-chi b´et ky-b´et toj ky-tx´otx´ n-chi ky-xo´n flechas kyi´j Orcos aye n-chi b´et ky-txlaj,
ex junjun kyxol qe jlu e kubʼ tzʼaq; extzun aye n-chi b´et kyi´j chej n-chi el ky-b´et ky-b´e ky-b´e
n-chi tzaq´wen kye ky-arco kye aj q´oj, aye n-chi ky-xo´n ky-q´ob´, mya n-chi ky-ok ky-xob´il tu´n ky-k´u´n. B´aj jlu
nim maj, extzen toj jun amb´il e kub´ tz´aq flechas kyxol Isengarders. Jun kyxol qe jlu,
noq twitz Pippin, kub´ t-xo´n tib´ ex mya jaw we´ juntl majl.
 Tzaj qonik´an exttzen aye Riders n-chi b´et ky-okx toj q´oj. nim orcs otoq che kub´ tz´aq, noqtzun aye
bʼaj kabʼe syent xjal e kyaj ten. Toj t-xe qlolj aye orcos e pon toj jun witz. A
aye alero te k´ul n-chi tzaj laq´e´xix, b´alo mya mas te oxe estadios t-xilen, noqtzun aye
mya b´ant ky-xi´ye juntl majl. Otoq che ok tzoqpaj qe soldad kyibʼaj chej kyiʼj. Jun tal k´loj xjal mya b´i´n kye
t-xim Ugluk, extzen n-chi b´et t-xe t-xaq k´ul: noq ox n-chi meltz´aj.
