aye Whiteskins tz´il n-chi b´et ky-b´et. Niky´? Tkyaqil amb´il n-chin anq´ine, wajb´ile kye. Me
mya tu'n kyjaw sch'in ex mya tu'n cycolpet. ¡K´alo´nqe ky-qan!
 Aju mankbʼil plaj te kawbʼil bʼant mintiʼ qʼaqʼbʼil tkʼuʼj. Extzun a Pippin el tniky´ ti´j qa te
