'At junjun n-xjalile n-chi ky-ka´yin tze´nku tze jalin, extzen il ti´j tu´n tten jun ti´x nim toklen tun ky-jaw we´;
ex noq ch'in yol in che yolin. Extzun at junjun tze´ye n-chi b´et kyi´j ky-q´ob´, extzen nimku n-chi b´ant
yolina wuk´ile. Aye elves n-chi tzyet, ax tok, n-chi ky-jawsa´n tze´ extzen n-chi ky-xnaq´tza´n kye tun ky-yolin
extzen n-xnaq´tzan kyi´j ky-yol tze´. Kykyaqil amb´il n-chi ky-ajben tun ky-yolin tuk´e tkyaqil, aye ojtxi Elfos
ma ku tbinchan. Pero te tibajxi ul aju nintz klolj, ex e ic'x tibaj mar, ex ka i el oq
tuj chq'ajlaj najchak, ex ewan kyib', ex b'itzin b'itz kyi'j q'ij mya b'a'n
tzaja juntl majl. Mya juntl maj. ax tok, ax tok, at jun tze´ tzaj jun maj: tzajni
tzalu toj witz te Lune, extzen atzun t-xe t-xe t-xe q´ij.
