mas ik tza´n qe xjal mya b´a´n. Atzun jun techel tiʼj nya bʼaʼn tiʼchaq tzaj toj Nim Qlolj aju
mlay che ten twitz Qʼij; extzun aye orcos te Saruman n-chi b´ant ky-ik´x, maske n-chi el kyik´un. Ayine
n-ximana ti o b´ant tu´n? ¿Aqe xjal lu o che kubʼ tnajsaʼn, moqa o che ok tmojbʼaʼn qe kyyajil xjal
te Orcos ex kye xjal? ¡Atzun jun mya b´a´n q´eq!
 A Treebeard tzaj t-xo´n jun amb´il, tze´nku n-chi yolin junjun t-xilen,
subterráneo Entish malediction. 'Jun amb´il tzik´, n-xi tzyet tu´n n-ximane tza´n tten n-chi b´et aye orcos
tun n-ik´x toj n-k´ul tzaqpi´n, chij. 'Oʼkx toj ambʼil jaʼlo ma kubʼ nximane qa
A Saruman at tpaj, extzen tzaj t-xnaq´tza´n tkyaqil b´e, extzen
n-chi jyon kyi´j n-ewin. Ate extzen aye t-xjalil mya b´a´n n-chi b´inchan nya b´a´n jalin. tjaq´
fronteras n-chi ky-tx´emin tze´ – tb´anil tze. Junjun tze noq oʼkx kubʼ kytxʼemin ex
q´onxa tun t-xi´ t-xupin – orc-mischief aju; pero chʼixme kykyaqil in che kubʼ bʼyoʼn ex in chex qʼiʼn tuʼn t-xi qʼet kywa qʼaqʼ
te Orthanc. Kukx at jun sib´ n-jaw toj Isengard kyoj qe q´ij lu.
 ‹¡Kyqʼonxe malbʼil tiʼj, t-xeʼ ex tqʼabʼ! nim kyxol qe tze´ lu aye wamiwe aye txuk n-chi b´inchan wune
b´i´n ti´j t-xu´k ex acorn; nimku attaq ky-wi´ ky-wi´x aye n-chi naj te jumajx jalin.
extzen at junjun t-xaq t-xaq t-xaq ex t-xaq t-xaq tze´ jatumel ate´toq jun amb´il t-xaq tze´ n-b´itzin. Ayine
o che ten mintiʼ in che aqʼunan. Ma txi nqʼoʼne ambʼil tuʼn kykubʼ tzʼaq qe tiʼchaq. ¡Il tiʼj tuʼn tkubʼ weʼ!›.
 A Treebeard jaw we´ twitz t-watb´il tuk´e jun t-xupin, jaw we´, extzen tzaj t-xo´n tq´ob´
twitz mes. Aye vas te spik´un n-chi lu´lun extzen n-chi tzaj ky-sama´n kab´e t-xaq q´aq´. Attoq jun
in che qoptzʼaj ik tzaʼn qʼaqʼ qʼankyaq toj twitz, ex aju t-xbʼalun in bʼaj t-xbʼalumin tibʼ ik tzeʼn jun matij t-xbʼalun.
 ‹¡Kbʼel npaʼne!›. tzaj tq´ajq´ajel twi´. ‹Ex ktzajel wukʼile. B´a´n t-xi t-onina
weye. Ax ikx teya k-onil kye tamiwoya ikyjo; qu´n qa a Saruman mya n-ok q´o´n twitz ti´j
A Rohan extzen a Gondor k-okil jun ky-q´oj t-xe extzen twitz. Aye q-b´e n-chi b´et
junx – te Isengard!'
 'Ok qo ul tuk´ila, chi Merry. ‹Kbʼantel quʼne aju jaku bʼant quʼne›.
 'Oki!' chi Pippin. 'B´a´n tu´n tok nka´yine aju´ q´ob´ saq t-xi´ t-xo´n. wajb´ile tu´n
tenx tzalu, maske mya b´a´n tu´n n-b´inchene nim: mya b´a´n tu´n t-xi tzik´ tna´l wune Ugluk exttzen aye
t-xilen Rohan.
 'B´a´n! B´a´n!' chi Bebardo. ‹Pero in chin yoline jun rat. Mintiʼ tuʼn qok ten naj. a tiwe´
tzaj nim q´aq´. Il ti´j tu´n t-xi n-xob´a ex tu´n n-ximane; mas nya kwest tu´n t-xi tq´ajq´ajel twi´! twitzju tuʼn tbʼant
a.'
