 Xiʼ bʼetil toj arco ex kubʼ weʼ jun ambʼil tjaqʼ jbʼal in kuʼtz toj
b´echq´ijil. Yajxitl jaw tzeʼn ex xi t-xoʼn tibʼ, ex noq jaxku tumel in che kubʼ tzʼaq qe t-xaq aʼ
n-chi tzaj ky-spik´umal twitz tx´otx´ n-chi ky-spik´un tze´nku junjen chispa q´eq ex q´ankyaq. Ul
tzaj tmeltz´aj extzen kub´ t-ximan tib´aj watb´il juntl majl extzen tzaj t-xo´n tib´.
 Tej tik´ ch´in amb´il aye hobbits n-chi kyb´i´n juntl majl n-chi yolin. In noktoq ik tzeʼn
n-ajlan kyi´j t-q´ob´. 'Fangorn, Finglas, Fladrif, aye, aye,' tzaj t-xupin. 'A nya b´a´n
a t-xilen qa noq ch´inx q-k´ul, chij n-chi tzaj t-xnaq´tza´n kyi´j hobbits. ‹Oʼkx oxe
t-xelju tnejel Ents n-chi b´et toj k´ul twitz qlolj: noq o´kx weye,
Fangorn, extzen Finglas exttzen Fladrif – tun t-xi q´et ky-b´i Elvish; b´a´n tu´n t-xi tqana
kye Leaflock exttzen Skinbark qa mas b´a´n teya. extzen kye oxe Leaflock extzen
A Skinbark mya nim tajb´en te aq´untl lu. A Leaflock ma tz´ok te t-watl, ch´ixmi tze´, b´a´n tu´n t-xi tq´ama´na: a
ma tz´ok t-xnaq´tza´n tjunalx tmij t-watl toj tkyaqil amb´il
q´ijel tuk´e t-xaq k´ul t-xe tqan. N-chi kub´ t-xmo´n tuk´e t-xaq
ttzmal twi´. In jaw weʼtoq toj jbʼalil; pero toj amb´il ja´lo otaq tz´ok t-xob´il tun t-xi´ b´et
najchaq axpe ikx toj amb´il aju. A Skinbark n-chi anq´in toj t-xe witz toj tkub´ex q´ij te Isengard. Atzun jatumel
aju nya b´a´n nya b´a´n o tzaj. Tzaj k´ixb´isa´n kyu´n aye orcos, extzen nimku t-xjalil extzen
qe t-ẍneʼl tzeʼ o che kubʼ bʼyoʼn ex o che kubʼ xiten. O jax tuj kya'j
qe lugar, kyxol qe tzeʼ abedul mas in che tzalaj tiʼj, ex mlay kuʼtz. Noqtzun tu´nj, ayin
daresay jaku tz´ok nchmo´ne jun tb´anil k´lojin kye q-k´wal – qa jaku b´ant wu´ne
n-el kynik´e ti´j tajb´en; qa n-chi b´ant ky-jaw we´ye: mya jun xjal n-chi b´et t-xilen. jun b´is
noq chʼin qeye!›.
 ‹¿Tiquʼn chʼin kybʼet ateʼye ex o che anqʼine nim ambʼil toj tnam lu?›. xi tqanin Pippin.
‹¿O che kyim nim xjal?›.
 'Oh, mya!' chi Bebardo. ‹Mi jun o kyim tojxi, ik tzeʼn jaku txi tqʼamaʼna. Junjun
ma che kub´ tz´aq toj mya b´a´n amb´il kye nim ab´q´i, ax tok: extzen mas ma che ch´iy
tze-ish. Pero mintiʼ jun maj e ten nim qeye ex mintiʼ o chʼiy. at
myia Entings – myia k´wal, n-chi tq´ama´na, mya toj jun tajlal ab´q´i.
N-chi tka´yina, n-chi el kyi´j Entwives.
 ‹¡Nimxix bʼis!›. chi Pippin. ‹¿Tzeʼn tten e kyim kykyaqil?›.
 ‹¡Mintiʼ e kyim!›. chi Bebardo. ‹Mintiʼ jun maj xi nqʼamaʼne qa kyim. N-chi el kyi´j qu´n, xi nq´ama´ne. O qo el txalpaj
kye ex mlay che kanet quʼn». Xi t-xupin. 'N-ximane qa nim xjal b´i´n kye. Txix
aye b´itz ti´j ky-jyet aye Ents tun ky-b´itzin aye Entwives n-chi b´itzin kyxol elfos ex xjal
te Mirkwood te Gondor. Mya b´a´n tu´n ky-el naj ti´j kyk´u´j.
 'B´a´n, n-xob´e qa aye b´itz mya n-chi ul toj tkub´ex q´ij kyi´j witz tun ky-pon toj Shire,'
chi Merry. ‹¿Mlaype tzaj tqʼamaʼna juntl maj qeye, moqa mlay tzaj tqʼamaʼna jun kyxol qe bʼitz qeye?›.
 ‹Ax tok, ax tok kbʼantel wuʼne›, chi Treebeard, ik tzeʼn bʼaʼn ela toj twitz aju xjelbʼitz. ‹Pero mlay bʼant wuʼne
q’manxa tojxix tumel, noq toj ch’in yol; ex yajxitl il tiʼj tuʼn tkubʼ bʼaj qyol: nchiʼj at qe
consejos tun ky-txko´n, extzen aq´untl tun t-xi b´inchen, extzen b´a´n jun b´e tun t-xi tzyet.
 ‹Atzun jun txʼolbʼabʼil nya bʼaʼn ex bʼisbʼajil›, chi xjal tej tkubʼ weʼ chʼin ambʼil. ‹Aj ttzaj twitz txʼotxʼ
tzmatoq ku´xun, extzen aye k´ul t-xe´l extzen t-xew, aye Ents extzen aye Entwives – extzen
atqe Entmaidens toj amb´il aju: ah! aju t-xtalb´il Fimbrethil, te Wandlimb aju
lightfooted, toj q´ij te q-ku´xun! – n-chi b´et junx extzen n-chi b´et
junx. Extzun aye q-k´u´j mya n-chi ch´iy toj junx tten: aye Ents xi kyq´o´n ky-
k´ujlalil kyi´j ti´chaq n-chi ky-ok ky-b´i´n twitz tx´otx´, extzen aye Entwives xi kyq´o´n ky-xim kye txqantl
cosas, tuʼnj aj Ents cycʼujlaʼn ke matij tzeʼ; ex qe kʼul toj chqʼajlaj, ex qe t-xe aʼ
qe witz maʼ kywaʼlil; ex n-chi k´an kyi´j a´ t-xe witz, extzen noq twitz awal n-chi wa´n tze´nku
qe tzeʼ in che kubʼ tzʼaq toj kybʼe; extzen n-chi xnaq´tzan kyi´j Elfos extzen n-chi yolin kyi´j tze´.
Atzun qe Entwives xi kyqʼoʼn kyximbʼetz kyiʼj qe tzeʼ chʼin kybʼet, ex kyiʼj qe tal tzeʼ ateʼ toj
q´ij twitz ky-qan k´ul; ex o cyil aju sloe tuj chk'ul, ex aju
manzana te k´ul extzen aye cerezo n-chi tzaj t-xmakal toj amb´il te q´ijel, extzen aye tze´n t-xmakal toj
