¿n-chi b´eta wuk´ile, tky´ajal Arathorn? B´a´n t-xi q-b´inchen jun b´e, moqa n-ku b´inchen jun b´e
jun b´ajsb´il t-xilen jun b´itz – qa at jun n-chi kyaj ten tun t-b´itzin qi´j t-xe´l.
 'Chin b´ete tuk´ila, chi Aragorn.
 Tzaj tk'o'n Jesús tk'olbil, ajtz meltz'aj cytxlaj muro, ex ic'x ti'jele cycyakil cytx'otx'e.
