extzen aye t-xaq tze´ mya b´i´n noq kab´e estadios jaqet. Atzun ja'lo
tzaj ky-xob´a aye t-xjalil Saruman, tu´n ky-xob´il te rey extzen tu´n ky-xob´il kye tze.
N-chi b´et ky-b´et toj ttzi ja te Helm tzmaxi tej t-xi´ ky-b´aj tkyaqil twitz Dike,
pero tjaq´ t-xe´ n-chi b´aj ky-b´uyin kyib´aj tze´nku junjen txuk n-chi b´aj ky-b´et. Noqx gan n-chi b´et ky-b´et extzen
n-chi b´et kyi´j t-xaq ja te coomb, n-chi jyon tumel tun ky-el oq. Toj tjawitz q´ij nimxix
