aju tten twitz tx'otx'. Mintiʼxix xi qqʼoʼne qwiʼye tiʼjju at tiʼjxi tmojonil qtxʼotxʼe.
Aye b´itz atqe n-chi yolin kyi´j tiyjil lu, noqtzun tu´nj, n-el naj ti´j qk´u´j, n-xi qq´o´n xnaq´tzb´il kye
noq kye k´wal, tza´n jun kostumbr mya b´a´n. Ex jaʼlo o che kuʼtz qe bʼitz kyxol
