jun, pero nqayin ti´j t-xe witz n-chi jaqet ky-kach. ky-chib´jel ky-q´ob´ ky-q´ob´ tze´nku
t-xaq lans, ky-q´ob´ ky-q´ob´ tze´nku junjen kuchiy. Kyxol attaq jun ch'in najb'il, ex
