aye b´inchal txuk n-chi b´ant ky-xnaq´tzan kyi´j tzaq´web´il kye ky-ch´in ky-b´inchb´en. N-qo jyon ti´ja tze´nku
najchaq t-xe k´ul, noqtzun ayetzi´n atx nim tiyjil n-chi wajb´ile tun n-b´i´ne axix tok ti´j.
