Wizard's Vale, aye Ents tuk´e kykyaqil ky-Huorns n-chi b´et t-xe´. Mintiʼtoq in che ok qkeʼyine,
ax tok, pero tkyaqil kyq´iq´ nojni tu´n t-xupin. Nimtoq qlolj, jun qonikʼan nim muj.
