 'Treebeard extzen junjuntl Ents n-chi b´et ky-b´et, ttxlaj ky-witze aye nim
ttzi ja. A Pippin extzen ayen ato´ye tuk´e. O qo kub´ qe´ye tib´aj t-xu´k Treebeard, extzen ayen
