tkyaqil otoq che aqʼunanxix toj tjawitz qʼij, in che kyaj ten nqayin ik tzeʼn jakutoq kanet jun
b´e tun t-xi´ya toj t-xe´chil aju´ t-xaq witz lu. pero tkyaqil maj n-chi kanet kye
twitz t-xe´chil, t-xe´l ex mya b´a´n t-xi´n, n-chi b´aj t-xmo´n twitz twitz tx´otx´ tjaq´; twitz t-xe
aye t-xaq t-xaq t-xaq n-chi kub´ t-ximan toj junjen marshes jatumel myia jun ti´x n-chi b´et extzen mya jun chyu´j
tuʼn tok qkeʼyin.
 Aye hobbits n-chi kub´ we´ t-xe jun witz nim twa´l, mya b´a´n ky-b´is extzen ky-b´is, ky-qan n-chi b´aj ky-b´inchen
q'aqmujil; extzen t-xe ky-witz n-chi tzaj ky-q´ob´ aye witz b´aj ky-b´aj ky-b´inchen jun muj n-chi b´et. jun chill
tzaj kyq'iq' tzajni toj tjawitz q'ij. In noktoq qonikʼan tibʼaj txʼotxʼ mintiʼ t-xilen kywitz;
