chij. ‹Ex aju t-xaq lu in xi laqʼeʼ toj bʼanqʼabʼaj. N-chi b´ant n-we´ye axtzun mya jun t-xilen.
Ok chin–' aye tyol n-chi kub´ t-xiten.
 A qlolj n-chi b´et t-xe´, jalin n-chi chmet nim t-xew, n-chi tzaj t-xo´n toj tjawitz q´ij extzen
xi t-xupin kya´j. Attoq jun t-xmakal q´ankyaq t-xe t-xe twi´. Searing
tzaj t-xob´il q´aq´ kyi´j witz. Tzajtzun jun kyq'iq' jb'al wen, ex junx tuk'il;
