piscinas tej t-xi q´aq´in aye q´aq´. N-chi kub´ ky-k´u´n toj kykyaqil a´, ky-witze q´eq, extzen t-xe´l
tjaq’ a’ qlolj. N-chi wile: ky-witz nya b´a´n extzen mya b´a´n ky-witz, extzen ky-witz b´a´n extzen ky-b´is.
nim ky-witz n-chi ky-ok ky-b´i´n extzen ky-b´a´n ky-b´a´n, extzen ky-chib´jel nya b´a´n ky-wi´. pero kykyaqil nya b´a´n, kykyaqil nya b´a´n, kykyaqil
kyimna. jun spik´un tz´aq at toj ky-k´u´j. A Frodo tzaj t-xmo´n twitz toj tq´ob´. ‹Mintiʼ bʼiʼn wuʼne alkyeqe
Eye; pero n-ximane qa n-ka´yine xjal ex elfos, extzen orcos ky-txlaj.
 'Ax tok, ax tok, chi Gollum. 'Kykyaqil kyimni, kykyaqil tzqij. Elfos ex xjal ex orcos. Aye kyimni
Marshes. At jun nin q´oj otaq tzik´, ax tok, kyja´tzun xi kyq´ama´n te tej t-xi´ Smeagol
tzmatoq ku´xun, tej tzmatoq ku´xun qine tej na´mxtoq tul aju Precious. jun nintz q´oj. Nimin twe
Aye xjal tuk´e ky-espada nim, extzen aye elfos nya b´a´n, extzen aye orcos n-chi ẍch´in. E q´ojin kyi´j
t-xe´chil toj junjun q´ij ex junjun xjaw toj Black Gates. Extzun aye marshes ma chi ch´iy atxix toj ab´q´i
yajxitl, xi kywa´n qe muqb´il; kukx n-chi b´et, n-chi b´et.
 'Pero atzun jun ab´q´i extzen mas t-xe´, chi Sam. ‹¡Aqeju kyimni mlay che ten ax tok! ¿Atzun
junjun nya b´a´n n-chi ul itz´j toj tx´otx´ qlolj?'
 ‹¿Alkye bʼiʼn tuʼn? Smeagol mya b´i´n, chi Gollum tzaj ttzaq´we´n. ‹Mlay bʼant tuʼn tpona kyukʼil;
mlay che ok tmaco'na. O tz´ok tilil qu´n jun maj, ax tok, nim toklen, jun maj o tz´ok tilil wu´ne; atzun kyeye mlay b'ant kyu'ne
tz´okxa kye. Noq o´kx qe tilb´ilal tun t-xi qka´yin, b´a´n, mya tun t-xi qmako´n. ¡Mya nim toklen! Kykyaqil kyimni.
 A Sam tzaj tka´yin toj qlolj extzen tzaj t-xob´il juntl maj, n-ximen qa tzaj t-ximin tiqu´n
A Smeagol otaq tz´ok tilil tu´n t-xi tmako´n kye. ‹Bʼaʼn, nya waje tuʼn tok nkeʼyine›, chi. 'Layx
