aye hobbits mya b´ant ky-b´i´n extzen mya b´ant ky-b´i´n ti n-chi b´isun ti´j. Extzun jun rat naj kykyaqil oxe e kub´ we´,
q´uqb´il ex b´i´n. Te Frodo exttzen Sam ikyjo tze´nku n-chi kyb´i´n, najchaq, jun
