nya b´a´n. Xi´ t-xo´n tib´aj xjaw, extzen tuk´e jun tq´ajq´ajel twi´ n-chi b´et toj tkub´ex q´ij,
n-chi b´et twitz kyq´iq´ toj t-xew.
 E kub´ tz´aq twitz, n-chi b´et ky-b´is twitz tx´otx´ t-xew. Pero aju t-xlekumal xobʼajil
n-chi b´et extzen n-meltz´aj, n-chi ik´x t-xe jalin, t-xe ky-witz, n-chi b´aj t-xupin a´ fen-reek
