a tq´oj Sauron; extzen t-xe´l a kyq´iq´ n-chi tzaj t-xo´n, n-chi kyaj ttzaqpi´n aye Dead Marshes
tzqij ex b´isb´ajil. Aju tz´is, tzmax t-xilen t-xilen twitz, axpe ikx tzmax najchaq
t-xob´il kye witz, tzaj t-xob´il tuk´e t-spik´umal xjaw.
 A Frodo extzen a Sam e jaw we´, n-chi ky-tx´u´n ky-witz, tze´nku junjen k´wal n-chi jaw we´ ti´j jun mya b´a´n
