tu´n t-xi tq´ama´n, qa ma chin ok tka´yin jalin! nim maj n-chi kyq´ama´n qa n-chi b´aj jun mya b´a´n, qa mya n-xi n-ka´yine n-b´ete,
bʼant tuʼn. Atzun ja'lo minti' in ximan wu'ne tu'n t-xi nka'yine juntl maj aju tij xjal. Kb´el tna´n t-xnaq´tzb´il
b´a´n tu´n t-xi nq´ama´ne te, Sam: mas aju q´aq´b´il tk´u´j. B´a´n tu´n t-xi tq´ama´n weye tkyaqil amb´il
otaq tz´ok t-xew, noqwit n-ku n-ka´yine juntl majl t-xmilal. pero il ti´j tu´n t-xi n-tx´jo´ne ​​tnejel,
qa mya tu'n mi'n tok tojtzqi'n weye.
