aju mas matij kyxol kykyaqil,
Nimxix, ojtxi, ex nim.
qa ma chin ok tojtzqi´na
Mlay chin el naj tiʼj tkʼuʼja.
Qa mya b´ant tu´na,
Mlay kub' kyximane qa ax tok;
Extzun ayin Oliphaunt,
extzen myia n-chin sb´une.
 'Atzun,' chi Sam, tej t-xi´ t-xnaq´tza´n, 'atzun jun t-xilen q-yol at quk´il toj
Shire. Nonsense b´a´n, extzen b´a´n mya. Extzun at qe q-yolb´il, extzen tqanil tzajni toj
a Sur, b´i´n tza´n. Toj amb´il ojtxi´ aye hobbits n-chi b´ettoq toj ky-b´e jalin extzen
 168
ju majt. Mya nim xjal n-chi meltz´aj, extzen mya noq tkyaqil n-chi kyq´ama´n n-ok q´uqe´ kyk´u´j ti´j: tqanil
te Bree, extzen mya b´a´n t-xilen Shiretalk, tze´n n-chi kyq´ama´n. pero o tz´ok nb´i´ne junjun tx´olb´ab´il ti´j
nim xjal twitz tx´otx´ toj Sunlands. Swertings n-chi q-b´i´n kye toj q-yolb´il; ex n-chi b´et kyi´j chej
kyi´j oliphaunts, 'tis tq´ama, aj ky-q´ojin. Xi kyqʼoʼn ja ex qe torre tibʼaj
oliphauntses ky-xu´k extzen kykyaqil, extzen aye oliphaunts n-chi ky-xo´n ab´j extzen tze´n kyxolx.
Kyja´tzun tej t-xi tq´ama´na "Aye xjal tzajniqe toj sur, kykyaqil ky-xb´alun q´an ex q´anpwaq;" xi nq´ama´ne "atpe jun
oliphaunts?" Qu´n qa at, n-chi b´et n-ka´yine, n-xi´ye t-xilen moqa mya. Exttzen ja´lin mya
q´manxa qa ok n-ka´yine jun oliphaunt. Bʼalo mintiʼ jun txkup ik tzeʼn jlu. Xi t-xupin.
 'Mya, mya oliphaunts,' chi Gollum juntl majl. A Smeagol mya b´i´n kyi´j. N-b´ant tu´n
mya kyaj tu´n ky-ka´yin. Nya taj tuʼn kyten. Smeagol taj tu´n t-xi´ najchaq ti´j
tzalu extzen t-xmoxina toj juntl najb´il mas nya b´a´n. Smeagol taj tu´n t-xi´ t-xnaq´tzb´en. tb´anil t-xnaq´tzb´en, mya b´a´n
tzaja tuk´e Smeagol?
 A Frodo jaw we´. Otaq tze´n toj tmij tkyaqil t-xob´il tej t-xi´ Sam
aju ojtxi b´itz te q´aq´ te Oliphaunt, extzen aju tze´n otaq tz´el ttzaqpi´n te t-xob´il.
'B´a´n tu´n tten jun mil oliphaunts qu´n tuk´e Gandalf tib´aj jun saq toj ky-wi´,'
ma tma. 'Yajxitl n-chi b´ant t-xi q-b´inchen jun b´e toj tx´otx´ mya b´a´n lu, b´a´n. Extzun mya; noq qex
tqan q´eq, noq o´kx. B´a´n, Smeagol, a toxin t-xilen jaku tz´ok te tb´anil. chin ule tuk´e
Aya.'
 ‹¡Bʼaʼn xnaqʼtzal, xnaqʼtzal at tnabʼil, tbʼanel xnaqʼtzal!›. tzaj tq´ajq´ajel Gollum tuk´e tzalajb´il, n-chi t-xupin Frodo
tqan. ¡B´a´n t-xnaq´tzb´en! Yajxitl, che ojlane jalin, b´a´n hobbits, tjaq´ t-xlekumal ab´j,
tz´apin tjaq´ ky-ab´j! Q´onk ojlal ex q´onk t-xob´a, tzmaxi aj t-xi´ t-xi´n aju´ twitz q´ankyaq. Yajxitl qe
b´a´n t-xi´ jun rat. ¡B´a´n ex jun rat ik tza´n qe t-xlekumal il ti´j tu´n qok!
