a tx´otx´ mya b´i´n, b´alo a b´ajsb´il wab´j n-chi wa´n junx. Junjun kye
ky-wa te Gondor n-chi wa´n, extzen junjen wafers te pan te b´e kye elfos, extzen n-chi ky-k´an jun
b´otz´. Extzun ti´j ky-a´ n-chi ky-k´u´n extzen noq n-chi ky-k´amo´n tun t-xi ky-q´o´n ky-a´
ttzi´.
 ‹N-xjelb´itze jtoj kkanet aʼ quʼne juntl maj?›. chi Sam. 'extzun n-ximane qa axpe ikx atztzu
n-chi k´an? Aye orcos n-chi k´an, ¿ikyjo?
