 Xi tka´yin Gollum kyi´j. jun t-xim mya b´a´n tzaj t-xilen twitz t-xmilal extzen tzaj t-wa´n.
A t-spik´umal n-el tpa´n twitz, extzen n-chi tzaj t-spik´umal twitz, extzen n-chi tzaj t-spik´umal, ma chi tijin ex ma chi sikt. jun spasmo
te k´ixk´oj n-chi tzaj t-xob´il, extzen n-chi meltz´aj, n-chi tka´yin juntl majl twitz t-xe´chil,
